title: Shishuvan dominate Distrixt Sports Office volleyball
text: Shishuvan (Matunga) dominated the District Sports Office inter-school volleyball tournament at their schoolâ€™s sports pavillion recently. The Matunga school won the girls U-14, boys U-14 and boys U-17 titles under coach Dhiraj Dubey. In the girls U-14 final, they beat CJ HS (Tardeo) 25-14, 25-17. In the boys U-14 final, they beat RRM Municipal (Charni Road) 25-14, 25-14, and in the boys U-17 final they beat CJ High School 25-15, 25-15.
